rComments: Marla is awesome. She is so enthusistic about art in an non-condescending manner (unlike the generic art prof). Really down to earth and genuinely wants to help but you have to have consistent attendance and be a talker to be her favorite (which isn't hard)
Good prof, presents material in clear manner and is really fun to be around. She's usually all smiley and is sweet and friendly.
Marla is very friendly and truely helpful. She is fair with marking and has a diverse knowledge in drawing, sculpture and some painting.
